      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ARMATREE ASAFA (8) has a strong record this trip with four wins and four placings from 12 starts. Recorded a 8 length win (30.23) in a Mix last time at this track. Rates a leading player. DURAN STING (2) made light work of a wide draw last time with a slick early sectional but gathered in and had to settle for the minors, finishing third (23.08) at Richmond over 401m. The form from her last run stacks up well. Will give a great sight again. WONGABOORI BELLE (7) doesn't win out of turn but recent form sound. Finished third (30.31) at Dubbo last time making it two minors on end. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Can measure up. JOHNNY DEXTER (5) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.",
